# Daily Diary - Day 04

## Loops & Iteration

### Today's Topics
- for loop
- while loop
- do-while loop
- Enhanced for loop
- break and continue

### Practical Work
- Printed patterns using nested loops
- Created number guessing game
- Implemented factorial calculation
- Practiced with arrays and loops

### Code Example
```java
public class LoopsDemo {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        // for loop
        for (int i = 1; i <= 5; i++) {
            System.out.println("Count: " + i);
        }
        
        // while loop
        int j = 1;
        while (j <= 5) {
            System.out.println("While: " + j);
            j++;
        }
    }
}
